name: Mamba Focus 'Metallic Gold'
description: Nike's Mamba Focus symbolizes Kobe Bryant's on-court transition to his alter ego. Updated in September 2019, this edition mimics a snake's metamorphosis in an embossed textile upper constructed with film overlays, an external heel cage and TPU eyelets inspired by reptilian eyes. Bryant's emblem on the tongue and a Swoosh outrigger are done in metallic gold. The sneaker utilizes a Zoom Air-boosted midsole and icy translucent rubber outsole.

name: Mamba Focus 'White Gum'
description: Kobe Bryant said, ‘[‘Mamba Mentality’ is] a constant quest to try to be better today than you were yesterday.’ Building on Bryant's signature line with Nike, the Mamba Focus ‘White Gum’ sneaker is replete with performance technology, featuring an external heel cage and Zoom Air cushioning. The snakeskin-inspired silhouette echoes the transition and metamorphosis Bryant overcame as an NBA phenom and reminds athletes to embrace their inner 'Mamba Mentality.'

name: Mamba Focus 'Black'
description: Known as one of the greatest basketball players of all time, Kobe Bryant led the Los Angeles Lakers to five NBA championships and won the MVP award in 2008. Bryant’s self-proclaimed ‘Black Mamba’ moniker became the name for his signature collaboration with Nike. Numerous silhouettes have joined the Mamba line, including the March 2019 reveal of the Mamba Focus ‘Black.’ This rendition is complete with a low-profile construction and snakeskin-inspired outsole.

name: Mamba Focus 'Lakers'
description: Revealed in August 2019, the Nike Mamba Focus 'Lakers' pays homage to Kobe Bryant's time leading the Los Angeles squad in jersey-inspired colors. The sneaker is clad in a black embossed upper— inspired by a snake’s metamorphosis—with purple tongue branding, a molded external heel cage and bright medial Swoosh. A Zoom Air midsole and split-colored rubber outsole promote a responsive reaction and control on the court.
